item.description: Currently pulling an all-nighter because kid left chewing gum out, and now I have to keep vigil for xylitol poisoning in the wienerdog. The dog is doing well, but I am fading. Time for a Diet Mountain Dew and some quality time with my Emacs config until dawn. #Emacs #Dogs #AllNighter
